***_ Failures and schedules
** DatabricksNotebook
***_ Execution, creation
***_ Modification events
** DatabricksSQL
***_ SQL warehouse operations
***_ Query-related events
** DatabricksUnityCatalog
***_ Catalog/schema/table access
***_ Data access audit
